<h3 id="Istall_graphical_standard_gnome_GUI">Istall graphical standard gnome GUI</h3>
<span class="anchor" id="line-254"></span><p class="line867"><span class="anchor" id="line-255"></span><span class="anchor" id="line-256"></span><pre><span class="anchor" id="line-1-30"></span>sudo apt-get install ubuntu-desktop ubuntu-restricted-extras</pre><span class="anchor" id="line-257"></span><span class="anchor" id="line-258"></span><p class="line867">
<h3 id="Istall_graphical_kde_GUI">Istall graphical kde GUI</h3>
